Package: omu
Title: A Metabolomics Analysis R Package for Intuitive Figures and Convenient Metadata Collection
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Connor", "Tiffany", email = "crtiffany@ucdavis.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Facilitates the creation of intuitive figures to describe metabolomics data by utilizing KEGG hierarchy data, and gathers functional orthology and gene data using KEGGREST to access the KEGG API.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
Imports:
    plyr,
    dplyr,
    stringr,
    KEGGREST,
    BiocInstaller,
    reshape2,
    ggfortify,
    ggplot2,
    magrittr,
    tidyr
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1.9000
